text: Prathista is a Telugu actress who primarily acted in Telugu movies. She rose to fame when she acted in the remake of 1972 Malayalam movie Rasaleela of the same name. Her list of prominent Telugu movies include Swapna Sundari, To Let, Aata Modalaindi, and Chethilo Cheyyesi. ==References== Category:Indian film actresses Category:Actresses in Telugu cinema Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
